    <Placemark>
      <name>Claridge's X The Newt</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>Claridge's X The Newt</b><br><i>Arts &amp; Culture</i><br>Wed 27th May – Sun 31st May<br>Claridge’s, Mayfair<br>Check site<br><br>Claridge’s collaborates with The Newt in Somerset, featuring a six-meter sculptural installation, willow sculptures, and 800 apples in a hallway display. Menus at Claridge’s will include ingredients from The Newt’s estate.<br><br><a href="https://www.cntraveller.com/gallery/things-to-do-in-london-this-weekend">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#orange-dot.png</styleUrl>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>-0.1475256,51.5125194,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>London Never Sleeps</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>London Never Sleeps</b><br><i>Nightlife</i><br>Wed 27th May<br>The London Cabaret Club<br>from £52.47 – £196.60<br><br>Experience a glamorous evening at The London Cabaret Club with a sumptuous dinner, live DJ, and performances inspired by British espionage. Enjoy talented singers, dancers, and specialty acts all night long.<br><br><a href="https://www.designmynight.com/london/event-space/holborn/the-london-cabaret-club/london-never-sleeps">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
