      <description><![CDATA[<b>Little Venice – the pursuit of pleasure</b><br><i>Arts &amp; Culture</i><br>Thu 28th May<br>Warwick Avenue tube station, Little Venice<br>£20<br><br>Explore Little Venice and the canal towpath, discovering remnants of the Age of Canals along the way. This walk offers a glimpse into the area's rich history.<br><br><a href="https://www.ianvisits.co.uk/calendar/weekend/">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
